#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:45 includes/class-jc-settings.php:147
msgid "Title"
msgstr "标题"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:46
msgid ""
"Recommended format: <code>Model number + core product keywords + "
"specifications/attributes</code>"
msgstr "推荐格式: <code>型号 + 核心产品词 + 规格/属性</code>"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:51
msgid "Short Description"
msgstr "短描述"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:53
#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:68
msgid "Writing Guidelines:"
msgstr "写作指南："

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:55
msgid ""
"The short description should naturally include high-frequency user search "
msgstr "简短描述应该自然地包含高频用户搜索"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:55
msgid "keywords"
msgstr "关键词"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:55
msgid " or "
msgstr "货"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:55
msgid "long-tail keywords"
msgstr "长尾关键词"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:56
msgid "Place important keywords at the beginning to improve keyword weighting"
msgstr "将重要关键词放在开头以提高关键词权重"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:57
msgid "Recommended length is between "
msgstr "建议长度介于"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:57
msgid "100-160"
msgstr "100-160"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:57
msgid " characters, providing sufficient value without being overly lengthy"
msgstr "字符，提供足够的价值，但又不会太长"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:58
msgid ""
"Use clear and concise language, avoiding excessive technical terminology"
msgstr "使用清晰简洁的语言，避免过多的技术术语"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:59
msgid ""
"Highlight unique product advantages, such as materials, performance, price, "
"usage scenarios, etc."
msgstr "突出产品独有的优势，比如材质、性能、价格、使用场景等。"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:70
msgid ""
"It is recommended to use relevant keywords in the details, no less than 5 "
"times, evenly distributed throughout the page."
msgstr "建议在详情中使用相关关键词，不少于5次，均匀分布于整个页面。"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:71
msgid ""
"Replace all pronouns in the details with keywords - use specific names "
"instead of words like \"it\" whenever possible."
msgstr ""
"用关键词替换详细信息中的所有代词 - 尽可能使用具体名称而不是“它”之类的词。"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:72
msgid "Each paragraph in the details should not exceed "
msgstr "详细信息中的每个段落不应超过"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:72
msgid "500"
msgstr "500"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:72
msgid ""
" characters. If exceeded, split into paragraphs. The full text should have a "
"minimum of "
msgstr "字符。如果超过，则拆分成段落。全文至少应包含"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:72
msgid "1000"
msgstr "1000"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:72
msgid " characters."
msgstr " 字符。"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:73
msgid ""
"Ensure original content in the details. Do not copy directly from the "
"internet. Page similarity within the website should not exceed "
msgstr "确保内容细节原创。请勿直接从互联网复制。网站内页面相似度不得超过 "

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:73
msgid "30%"
msgstr "30%"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:73
msgid "."
msgstr "。"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:82
msgid "Category Selection Guidelines:"
msgstr "类别选择指南："

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:84
msgid ""
"Select the most relevant categories for your product to improve "
"discoverability."
msgstr "为您的产品选择最相关的类别以提高可发现性。"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:85
msgid "Use specific categories rather than generic ones when possible."
msgstr "尽可能使用特定类别而不是通用类别。"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:86
msgid ""
"Avoid selecting too many categories - 2-4 relevant categories are "
"recommended."
msgstr "避免选择太多类别 - 建议选择 2-4 个相关类别。"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:87
msgid ""
"Check existing categories before creating new ones to maintain consistency."
msgstr "在创建新类别之前，请检查现有类别以保持一致性。"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:96
msgid "Tag Usage Guidelines:"
msgstr "标签使用指南："

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:98
msgid ""
"Use tags to highlight specific features, materials, or use cases of your "
"product."
msgstr "使用标签突出显示产品的特定功能、材料或用例。"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:99
msgid "Tags should be single words or short phrases separated by commas."
msgstr "标签应该是用逗号分隔的单个单词或短语。"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:100
msgid "Focus on important keywords that customers might search for."
msgstr "关注客户可能搜索的重要关键词。"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:101
msgid ""
"Avoid duplicate tags and excessive tagging - 5-10 relevant tags are "
"sufficient."
msgstr "避免重复标签和过度标签 - 5-10 个相关标签就足够了。"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:108
msgid "Download"
msgstr "下载"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:110
msgid "Downloadable Content Guidelines:"
msgstr "可下载内容指南："

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:112
msgid "Upload high-quality files in supported formats (PDF, DOC, ZIP, etc.)."
msgstr "上传支持格式（PDF、DOC、ZIP 等）的高质量文件。"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:113
msgid "Ensure files are virus-free and safe for users to download."
msgstr "确保文件无病毒且可供用户安全下载。"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:114
msgid "Provide clear file descriptions to help users understand content."
